<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Kerupuk Kulit Sumbar – Perjalanan Rasa dari Lokal untuk Dunia</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --amber: #E8961F;
    --amber-light: #F5B84C;
    --amber-pale: #FDF3E0;
    --brown: #2C1810;
    --brown-mid: #5C3D2A;
    --cream: #FEFAF3;
    --green: #3D6B4A;
    --green-light: #E8F4ED;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --gray: #7A6C5D;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--brown);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; width: 100%; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(44,24,16,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 14px 5%;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: var(--amber-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--amber-light); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2C1810 0%, #5C3D2A 50%, #E8961F 100%);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 120px 5% 80px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(232,150,31,0.25) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 1100px; width: 100%;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px;
    align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 1;
  }
  .hero-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--amber);
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .hero h1 span { color: var(--amber-light); }
  .hero-desc {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--amber);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 14px 30px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--amber-light); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .btn-outline {
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 14px 30px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
  }
  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--amber-light); background: rgba(232,150,31,0.1); }

  /* Product image hero */
  .hero-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
  }
  .hero-img-glow {
    position: absolute; width: 350px; height: 350px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,150,31,0.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .hero-img {
    width: 100%; max-width: 400px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ── WAVE DIVIDER ── */
  .wave { display: block; width: 100%; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0; }
  .wave svg { display: block; }

  /* ── SECTION COMMON ── */
  section { padding: 90px 5%; }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--amber); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
    color: var(--brown);
    line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .section-desc {
    color: var(--brown-mid);
    font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  /* ── ABOUT ── */
  .about { background: var(--cream); }
  .about-inner {
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 70px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-img-stack {
    position: relative; height: 420px;
  }
  .about-card {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(44,24,16,0.18);
  }
  .about-card img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .about-card:nth-child(1) {
    width: 72%; height: 300px;
    top: 0; left: 0;
  }
  .about-card:nth-child(2) {
    width: 55%; height: 220px;
    bottom: 0; right: 0;
    border: 4px solid var(--cream);
  }
  .badge {
    position: absolute; bottom: 24px; left: -12px;
    background: var(--amber);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(232,150,31,0.4);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .pillars {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }
  .pillar {
    background: var(--amber-pale);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .pillar-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pillar h4 { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--brown); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .pillar p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── MISI STRIP ── */
  .misi-strip {
    background: var(--brown);
    padding: 70px 5%;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .misi-strip blockquote {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
    position: relative;
  }
  .misi-strip blockquote::before {
    content: '"';
    font-size: 5rem; color: var(--amber); opacity: 0.3;
    position: absolute; top: -30px; left: -20px;
    font-family: Georgia, serif; line-height: 1;
  }
  .misi-strip cite {
    display: block; margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 0.82rem; font-style: normal;
    color: var(--amber-light); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── PRODUK ── */
  .produk { background: var(--white); }
  .produk-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .produk-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 52px; }
  .produk-header .section-desc { margin: 0 auto; }
  .produk-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 28px;
  }
  .produk-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232,150,31,0.15);
    transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s;
    background: var(--cream);
  }
  .produk-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(44,24,16,0.12); }
  .produk-img {
    height: 220px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 4rem;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .produk-img > div[style*="position:absolute"] { z-index: 2; }
  .produk-img.balado { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FDEBD0, #F5B84C); }
  .produk-img.keju { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFF9E6, #FFE57A); }
  .produk-img.rumputlaut { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E8F5E9, #A5D6A7); }
  .produk-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .produk-body { padding: 22px 24px 28px; }
  .varian-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .tag-balado { background: rgba(232,66,31,0.1); color: #C0392B; }
  .tag-keju { background: rgba(232,192,31,0.15); color: #8B6914; }
  .tag-rumputlaut { background: var(--green-light); color: var(--green); }
  .produk-body h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .produk-body p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .harga {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .harga-val {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--amber);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .harga-gram {
    font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gray); margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .order-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--brown);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none; transition: background .2s;
  }
  .order-btn:hover { background: var(--amber); }

  /* ── KEUNGGULAN ── */
  .keunggulan { background: var(--amber-pale); }
  .keunggulan-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .keunggulan-header { max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .keunggulan-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px;
  }
  .keu-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 10px; padding: 28px 22px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--amber);
  }
  .keu-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .keu-card h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--brown); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .keu-card p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* ── KONTAK ── */
  .kontak { background: var(--brown); }
  .kontak-inner {
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .kontak .section-title { color: var(--white); }
  .kontak .section-label { color: var(--amber-light); }
  .kontak .section-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
  .kontak-list { margin-top: 32px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .kontak-item {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .kontak-icon {
    width: 40px; height: 40px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: rgba(232,150,31,0.15);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .kontak-item a { color: var(--amber-light); text-decoration: none; }
  .kontak-item a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .kontak-right {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px;
  }
  .kontak-right h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    color: var(--white); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .jam-ops {
    background: rgba(232,150,31,0.12);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);
    border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .jam-ops p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .jam-ops strong { color: var(--amber-light); }
  .maps-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    background: var(--amber); color: var(--white);
    padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.88rem;
    width: 100%; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px; transition: background .2s;
  }
  .maps-btn:hover { background: var(--amber-light); }
  .nib-btn {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.88rem;
    width: 100%; justify-content: center; transition: border-color .2s, color .2s;
  }
  .nib-btn:hover { border-color: var(--amber); color: var(--amber-light); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: #1A0E08;
    padding: 28px 5%;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }
  footer span { color: var(--amber); }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; }
    .hero-img-wrap { order: -1; }
    .about-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-img-stack { height: 280px; }
    .produk-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .keunggulan-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .kontak-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 580px) {
    nav { padding: 12px 4%; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .produk-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .keunggulan-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* Scroll fade-in */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease;
  }
  .fade-up.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Kerupuk Kulit Sumbar</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#about">Tentang</a>
    <a href="#produk">Produk</a>
    <a href="#keunggulan">Keunggulan</a>
    <a href="#kontak">Kontak</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-tag">🌟 Produk Baru Setiap Hari</div>
      <h1>Renyah.<br><span>Gurih.</span><br>Penuh Cinta.</h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        Kerupuk kulit sapi pilihan, tanpa pengawet, diolah dari hulu ke hilir
        langsung ke tangan Anda. Dari dapur lokal Sumatra Barat untuk seluruh Indonesia.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#produk" class="btn-primary">🛒 Lihat Produk</a>
        <a href="#kontak" class="btn-outline">Hubungi Kami</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-img-wrap">
      <div class="hero-img-glow"></div>
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"
           onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';"
           class="hero-img" alt="Kerupuk Kulit Sumbar">
      <div style="display:none; width:100%; max-width:400px; height:320px; border-radius:16px; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#E8961F,#5C3D2A); align-items:center; justify-content:center; box-shadow:0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); font-size:5rem; position:relative; z-index:1;">🫙</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Wave -->
<div class="wave" style="background:#2C1810;">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path d="M0,30 C360,60 1080,0 1440,30 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#FEFAF3"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-inner">
    <div class="about-img-stack fade-up">
      <!-- Visual placeholder stacks -->
      <div class="about-card" style="width:72%; height:300px; top:0; left:0;">
        <div style="width:100%; height:100%; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#F5B84C,#E8961F); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:4rem;">🐄</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card" style="width:55%; height:220px; bottom:0; right:0; border:4px solid #FEFAF3;">
        <div style="width:100%; height:100%; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#3D6B4A,#A5D6A7); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:3rem;">🏡</div>
      </div>
      <div class="badge">
        ✅ Tanpa Pengawet<br>
        🌿 Bahan Alami
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-up">
      <div class="section-label">Tentang Kami</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Usaha Rumahan yang<br>Berdedikasi untuk Anda</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Kerupuk Kulit Sumbar adalah usaha keripik kulit rumahan yang berdedikasi menghadirkan
        camilan sehat, gurih, dan renyah untuk keluarga Indonesia. Dibuat dari kulit sapi pilihan,
        tanpa pengawet, dan penuh cinta.
      </p>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-top: 16px;">
        Didirikan dengan keyakinan bahwa bisnis adalah sebuah perjalanan panjang yang bermakna —
        kami berkomitmen untuk terus berinovasi, menggerakkan ekonomi lokal, dan mengantarkan
        kebaikan nutrisi kulit sapi ke setiap sudut yang bisa kami jangkau.
      </p>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">🔗</div>
          <h4>Rantai Distribusi Ringkas</h4>
          <p>Langsung dari pengrajin ke konsumen, tanpa banyak perantara.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">🌾</div>
          <h4>Bahan Baku Berkualitas</h4>
          <p>Kulit sapi pilihan diolah menjadi bahan baku berkualitas tinggi.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">💚</div>
          <h4>Alami dari Hulu ke Hilir</h4>
          <p>Diolah secara alami tanpa pengawet buatan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">🌍</div>
          <h4>Lokal Mendunia</h4>
          <p>Karya lokal yang siap menjelajahi pasar yang lebih luas.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MISI STRIP -->
<div class="misi-strip">
  <blockquote class="fade-up">
    Perjalanan Rasa dari Lokal untuk Dunia — mengantarkan kebaikan bahan baku segar langsung dari sumbernya ke tangan konsumen global dengan kualitas terbaik.
    <cite>— Misi Kerupuk Kulit Sumbar</cite>
  </blockquote>
</div>

<!-- PRODUK -->
<section class="produk" id="produk">
  <div class="produk-inner">
    <div class="produk-header fade-up">
      <div class="section-label">Varian Produk Kami</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Kerupuk Kulit Sumbar</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Hadir dari komitmen untuk mengubah kerupuk kulit tradisional menjadi camilan modern
        dengan kelezatan aneka rasa yang begitu nyata, renyah, dan mencolok kualitasnya
        sejak gigitan pertama. Tersedia dalam 3 varian rasa pilihan.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="produk-grid">

      <!-- Balado -->
      <div class="produk-card fade-up">
        <div class="produk-img balado">
          <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" alt="Kerupuk Kulit Sumbar">
          <div style="position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;background:rgba(192,57,43,0.9);color:white;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:600;">🌶️ Balado</div>
        </div>
        <div class="produk-body">
          <span class="varian-tag tag-balado">Varian Pedas</span>
          <h3>Kerupuk Kulit Balado</h3>
          <p>Sensasi pedas-gurih khas masakan Minang yang menggugah selera. Balado autentik dari dapur Sumatra Barat.</p>
          <div class="harga">
            <div>
              <div class="harga-val">Rp 10.000</div>
              <div class="harga-gram">120 gram / bungkus</div>
            </div>
            <a href="https://wa.me/6282286058684?text=Halo%2C%20saya%20ingin%20memesan%20Kerupuk%20Kulit%20Balado%20120gr" class="order-btn" target="_blank">Pesan</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Keju -->
      <div class="produk-card fade-up" style="transition-delay:.1s">
